03:18.098 --> 03:21.090
- Yeah, just for a minute.
- I am.

03:22.102 --> 03:23.365
Look out, Fonz!

03:23.503 --> 03:26.234
- Fonz, you almost sat
on the floor. -Yeah.

03:26.373 --> 03:28.705
Everything is just a little
blurry right now, you know?

03:28.842 --> 03:30.776
