06:06.633 --> 06:08.226
- Oh, no.
- Oh, yeah.

06:08.368 --> 06:09.836
Boy, you're really hungry, huh?

06:09.970 --> 06:11.870
- Long time between feedings?
- Uh-huh.

06:12.005 --> 06:14.872
Okay, lamb is all carved.

06:15.008 --> 06:16.601
- MARION: Oh.
- RICHIE: Ah, great.

06:16.743 --> 06:18.837
Richie, would you like
to give some to Fonz?

06:18.979 --> 06:21.243
Sure. Can I, uh,
serve you some lamb, Fonz?

06:21.381 --> 06:24.180
- I'd rather do it myself, huh?
-(grunts)

06:26.119 --> 06:28.816
I think I hit a bone here.

06:30.824 --> 06:32.792
You did, Fonzie.

06:32.926 --> 06:36.590
Uh, would you just go
for a piece to the left, please?

06:36.730 --> 06:38.721
Just, uh, up and over.

06:40.467 --> 06:42.333
- JOANIE: Oh.
- How'd I do, huh?

06:42.469 --> 06:43.493
I got it, see?

06:43.637 --> 06:46.072
I told you I had no problem.

06:49.342 --> 06:51.606
More lamb, Fonz?

06:51.745 --> 06:54.646
No, I think I had sufficient.

06:54.781 --> 06:56.271
- Thanks.
- Okay.

06:56.416 --> 06:59.977
Mrs. C,
this is a most memorable meal.

07:00.120 --> 07:02.612
It was for me, too, Fonz.

07:02.756 --> 07:04.281
For all of us, Fonzie.

07:04.424 --> 07:06.688
Is-is it all right now if I just
kind of clear the table?

07:06.826 --> 07:08.419
- Oh, we'll-we'll take care
of the dishes. -No. -No.

07:08.561 --> 07:10.188
