07:14.034 --> 07:16.059
Oh, there's my date.

07:17.971 --> 07:19.632
Fonzie, you've got a date?

07:19.773 --> 07:20.865
- Yeah.
- Now, listen, Fonz, maybe

07:21.007 --> 07:22.566
