with us tonight.

07:22.709 --> 07:25.201
Hey, hey,
I handpicked this one myself.

07:27.047 --> 07:28.913
Is-is this chick dressed
all in white?

07:29.049 --> 07:30.414
RICHIE:
Yeah, she is.

07:30.550 --> 07:32.018
It's the right one.
All right.

07:32.152 --> 07:34.780
I'll see you later. Whoa.

07:36.256 --> 07:38.020
<i>RICHIE:
Another day, another dollar.</i>

07:38.158 --> 07:39.216
Of course, I'm not working,

07:39.359 --> 07:40.918
