giving me a dollar,

07:41.061 --> 07:42.551
but you know what I'm saying.

07:42.696 --> 07:44.027
Yeah.

07:44.164 --> 07:46.690
Yeah, it's just a great day
to be alive, isn't it?

07:46.833 --> 07:47.925
Yeah.

07:48.068 --> 07:50.036
Well, you ready
to start off the morning

07:50.170 --> 07:52.104
