07:52.238 --> 07:54.138
I'm not hungry.

07:54.274 --> 07:56.971
Oh. Well, that-that happens.

07:57.110 --> 07:58.976
I think I'm gonna get a bite.

07:59.112 --> 08:00.807
Uh, tell you what,
I'll bring you back some coffee.

08:00.947 --> 08:02.381
