again, an outside chance even.

08:42.655 --> 08:44.623
Well, there is.
My dad explained it to me.

08:44.758 --> 08:47.159
Now, listen, what Fonzie's got
is optic neuritis.

08:47.293 --> 08:51.730
And with treatments...
he could get his sight back.

08:51.865 --> 08:54.334
Ralph, that's wonderful news.

08:55.835 --> 08:57.462
But then again,
it could be permanent.

09:00.673 --> 09:03.404
All right, all right,
listen up. It's Fonzie!

09:03.543 --> 09:05.534
- All right.
