09:13.219 --> 09:15.984
Well, how does it feel to be
back at Arnold's, huh, Fonz?

09:16.122 --> 09:17.954
Yeah, everything's just
exactly the same.

09:18.091 --> 09:19.650
Oh, why don't we sit down here

09:19.793 --> 09:21.318
