or something, huh?

09:21.461 --> 09:22.792
Just-just right over here,

09:22.929 --> 09:24.829
just at our regular,
old, normal booth.

09:24.964 --> 09:26.932
There it is, Fonz.

09:27.067 --> 09:29.161
Good. There you go.

09:29.302 --> 09:31.202
Hi, Fonz.

09:31.337 --> 09:34.238
Hey. Al?

09:34.374 --> 09:36.365
How you doing, Al?

09:37.977 --> 09:40.878
Yeah, it's me, Al, your friend.

09:41.014 --> 09:43.984
("Vinéfli
The man who made you blind.

09:44.117 --> 09:46.381
Al, Al, Al, listen up.

09:46.519 --> 09:48.078
It's not your fault.

09:48.221 --> 09:51.122
I've been taking my chance
for years by eating here.

09:51.257 --> 09:53.521
(Richie chuckles)

09:53.660 --> 09:55.128
- Al?
- Yeah, Fonz?

09:55.261 --> 09:56.729
I want you
to do something for me.

09:56.863 --> 09:58.058
I'd do anything, Fonz.

09:58.198 --> 09:59.688
Do you want me to leave town?
I'll do it.

09:59.833 --> 10:01.267
You want me to adopt you?
I'll do it.

10:01.401 --> 10:03.995
- Al... -Do you want me
to shut up? I'll do it!

10:04.137 --> 10:06.538
Come here.

10:06.673 --> 10:09.904
