see, 'cause I have.

10:10.043 --> 10:11.909
You understand?

10:12.045 --> 10:14.605
Thanks, Fonz.

10:14.747 --> 10:16.442
If I only could.

10:19.519 --> 10:21.817
Fonz, ready to, uh, talk
to some more friends, huh?

10:21.955 --> 10:23.047
No.

10:23.189 --> 10:25.157
Look, uh,
Potsie and Ralph are over here.

10:25.291 --> 10:26.725
You just stay right here.
I'll get them.

10:26.860 --> 10:28.259
Hey, come on, guys.
Come on, talk to the Fonz, okay?

10:28.394 --> 10:30.055
He's right over here.
He really wants to talk to you.

10:30.196 --> 10:32.028
Oh, say hi to the Fonz for me,
Rich, okay?

10:32.165 --> 10:34.293
Say hi to him yourself.
He's right here.

10:34.434 --> 10:36.425
(Potsie chuckles faintly)

10:37.704 --> 10:39.672
Hi, Fonz.

10:39.806 --> 10:41.672
Uh...

10:41.808 --> 10:44.937
you see the new
Playboy centerfold?

10:49.182 --> 10:51.241
It wasn't very good, you know.

10:51.384 --> 10:54.115
