you've always got a good one.

11:02.328 --> 11:03.386
Yeah, yeah, come on here.

11:03.530 --> 11:05.862
- Yeah, come on.
- So true. So true.

11:05.999 --> 11:07.797
Okay, all right, all right.

11:07.934 --> 11:09.561
Here's an oldie, but a goodie.

11:09.702 --> 11:11.067
Oh, good. A goodie, okay.

11:11.204 --> 11:13.070
All right, what's this?
What's this?

11:13.206 --> 11:14.867
You give up? (laughs)

11:15.008 --> 11:17.602
That's a spider
doing pushups, huh? Uh...

11:21.514 --> 11:23.107
That's not really a funny joke.

11:23.249 --> 11:25.809
L-I didn't ever like that
that much.

11:25.952 --> 11:27.681
- Cunningham?
- RICHIE: Yeah, Fonz?

11:27.820 --> 11:29.185
- You here?
- I'm right here.

11:29.322 --> 11:31.723
- Get me out of here. -Oh, no,
you don't want to leave yet.

11:31.858 --> 11:33.155
