- Oh, yeah, Fonz, do the jukebox.
- Yeah, Fonz, you can do that.

11:43.870 --> 11:44.996
- Yeah, I can do that.
- He's gonna do it!

11:45.138 --> 11:46.299
- I can do that.
- All right, Fonz.

11:46.439 --> 11:47.600
-(cheering)
- All right, Fonzie!

11:47.740 --> 11:48.935
- I'll get you over there.
- Hey, hey, hey, hey.

11:49.075 --> 11:50.099
I can find it. I can find it.

11:50.243 --> 11:51.438
- All right.
- It's all right.

11:51.578 --> 11:52.739
Right.
Y-You're doing great, Fonz.

11:52.879 --> 11:54.369
- Hey, hey.
- He-He's gonna do it now.

11:54.514 --> 11:56.004
(excited chatter)

11:56.149 --> 11:57.639
All right, here you go, Fonz.

11:57.784 --> 12:00.219
- No one does it like you, Fonz.
- The tap. That's right.

12:00.353 --> 12:01.582
POTSIE:
All right. Hey.

12:01.721 --> 12:02.950
I could do this blindfolded.

12:03.089 --> 12:05.080
- RICHIE: That's right.
-(others chuckle)

12:12.865 --> 12:14.230
