sitting down yet, are you?

12:43.363 --> 12:45.229
Oh. No, Fonz.

12:45.365 --> 12:48.027
Could you find my knife, put
a little butter on it, please?

12:48.167 --> 12:50.067
JOANIE: Oh. I'll just
butter your roll, Fonz.

12:50.203 --> 12:51.329
FONZIE:
Thanks.

12:51.471 --> 12:53.337
You know, I remember
when I played intramural sports.

12:53.473 --> 12:54.634
There was one game

12:54.774 --> 12:56.936
-in touch football...
-ls there any salt on the table?

12:57.076 --> 12:58.976
